---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Grithos | A Philosophy of Life Built on Grit and Ethos"
  description="Grithos is a philosophy of life built on grit and ethos. Four pillars, twelve tenets, and 365 daily practices for living with moral courage, strength, and purpose."
  ogTitle="Grithos — A Philosophy of Life"
  ogDescription="Four pillars. Twelve tenets. 365 daily practices. A philosophy of life built on grit, ethos, and the moral courage to do right, regardless."
  ogUrl="https://grithos.com"
  canonical="https://grithos.com"
  activePage="home"
>

<style is:inline>
  /* ═══ HERO ═══ */
  .hero {
    min-height: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 60px 20px 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 40px 16px 32px; }
  }

  /* Radial glow behind logo */
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 45%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 800px; height: 800px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(196,168,130,.07) 0%, rgba(196,168,130,.03) 30%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    animation: pulse-glow 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Particle field */
  .hero-particles {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-particles { display: none; }
  }
  .particle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 2px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: float-up linear infinite;
  }
  .particle:nth-child(1) { left: 15%; animation-duration: 18s; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .particle:nth-child(2) { left: 30%; animation-duration: 22s; animation-delay: 3s; width: 1px; height: 1px; }
  .particle:nth-child(3) { left: 50%; animation-duration: 20s; animation-delay: 6s; }
  .particle:nth-child(4) { left: 65%; animation-duration: 25s; animation-delay: 2s; width: 3px; height: 3px; }
  .particle:nth-child(5) { left: 80%; animation-duration: 19s; animation-delay: 8s; width: 1px; height: 1px; }
  .particle:nth-child(6) { left: 25%; animation-duration: 24s; animation-delay: 5s; }
  .particle:nth-child(7) { left: 70%; animation-duration: 21s; animation-delay: 10s; width: 1px; height: 1px; }
  .particle:nth-child(8) { left: 40%; animation-duration: 23s; animation-delay: 7s; }
  .particle:nth-child(9) { left: 55%; animation-duration: 17s; animation-delay: 1s; width: 3px; height: 3px; }
  .particle:nth-child(10) { left: 85%; animation-duration: 26s; animation-delay: 4s; }
  .particle:nth-child(11) { left: 10%; animation-duration: 20s; animation-delay: 9s; }
  .particle:nth-child(12) { left: 90%; animation-duration: 22s; animation-delay: 11s; width: 1px; height: 1px; }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 16px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-logo-img {
    width: clamp(280px, 85vw, 800px);
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    animation: fade-in 1.5s ease-out 0.2s both;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(184,168,142,.25)) drop-shadow(0 0 80px rgba(184,168,142,.15)) drop-shadow(0 0 120px rgba(184,168,142,.08));
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 24px);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    animation: fade-in-up 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
  }

  .hero-pronunciation {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    animation: fade-in 1s ease-out 0.8s both;
  }

  .hero-gold-line {
    width: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    animation: expand-line 1.2s ease-out 1s forwards;
  }

  .hero-motto {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
    animation: fade-in-up 1s ease-out 1.2s both;
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .hero-motto-sub {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 24px);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
    animation: fade-in-up 1s ease-out 1.4s both;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    animation: fade-in 1s ease-out 2s both;
  }
  .hero-scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: pulse-glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ═══ ORIGIN ═══ */
  .origin {
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .origin-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 19px);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ═══ CREED ═══ */
  .creed {
    padding: 28px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .creed::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(196,168,130,.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .creed-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .creed-text {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  .creed-text .gold { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ═══ FOUNDATION ═══ */
  .foundation {
    padding: 28px 0;
  }
  .foundation-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ═══ FOUR PILLARS ═══ */
  .pillars {
    padding: 28px 0 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pillars-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }
  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .pillar-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(33,38,47,.9) 0%, rgba(28,32,41,.95) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    padding: 56px 44px;
    transition: all .4s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .pillar-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity .4s;
  }
  .pillar-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 60px rgba(196,168,130,.06), 0 0 1px rgba(196,168,130,.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .pillar-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .pillar-numeral {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(196,168,130,.12);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: .05em;
  }
  .pillar-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .22em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pillar-name {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: .01em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .pillar-tagline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: .01em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .pillar-divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-border), transparent);
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .pillar-body {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* ═══ TENETS ═══ */
  .tenets {
    padding: 28px 0 32px;
  }
  .tenets-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .tenets-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .tenets-pillar {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    padding: 40px 36px;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .tenets-pillar:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(196,168,130,.05);
  }
  .tenets-pillar-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .tenets-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .tenets-list li {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tenets-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .tenets-list li a {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 14px 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: color .2s, padding-left .2s;
  }
  .tenets-list li:last-child a {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .tenets-list li a:hover {
    color: var(--gold);
    padding-left: 8px;
  }
  .tenets-list li a span {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-right: 12px;
  }
  .tenets-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 56px;
  }
  .tenets-cta a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-border);
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all .3s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .tenets-cta a:hover {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .tenets-cta a svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
  }

  /* ═══ TODAY'S PRACTICE ═══ */
  .today-practice {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
  .today-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface) 0%, var(--card) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    padding: 52px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color .3s;
  }
  .today-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
  }
  .today-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 10%, var(--gold) 50%, transparent 90%);
    opacity: .7;
  }
  .today-date {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .today-tenet {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .today-text {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 26px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .today-link {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .today-link:hover {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
  .today-link svg {
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
    vertical-align: -2px;
    margin-left: 5px;
  }
  .today-forge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--void);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  @media(max-width:768px) {
    .today-card {
      padding: 36px 24px;
    }
  }

  /* ═══ SUBSCRIBE ═══ */
  .subscribe {
    padding: 28px 0 32px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .subscribe::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(196,168,130,.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .subscribe-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .subscribe-title {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: .01em;
  }
  .subscribe-sub {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .subscribe-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .subscribe-form input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 15px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-right: none;
    border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px;
    color: var(--white);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .3s, box-shadow .3s;
  }
  .subscribe-form input[type="email"]::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .subscribe-form input[type="email"]:focus {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(196,168,130,.1);
  }
  .subscribe-form button {
    padding: 14px 28px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--void);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .3s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .subscribe-form button:hover {
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.85;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(196,168,130,.3);
  }
  .subscribe-success {
    display: none;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .subscribe-error {
    display: none;
    color: #c47070;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .subscribe-form {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .subscribe-form input[type="email"] {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .subscribe-form button {
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  }

  /* ═══ FOUNDER ═══ */
  .founder {
    padding: 28px 0 32px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .founder-photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .founder-photo {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color .3s;
  }
  .founder-photo-wrap:hover .founder-photo {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
  }
  .founder-photo-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,168,130,.15);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .founder-name {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .founder-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .founder-detail {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .founder-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-border);
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .founder-cta:hover {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ═══ RESPONSIVE ═══ */
  @media(max-width:768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: 90vh;
      padding: 28px 0 24px;
    }
    .pillars-grid,
    .tenets-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .pillar-card {
      padding: 40px 28px;
    }
    .tenets-pillar {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
    .pillar-numeral {
      font-size: 40px;
    }
    .pillar-name {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-particles">
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <img src="/assets/images/grithos-logo.png" alt="Grithos — Grit. Ethos. Grithos." class="hero-logo-img">
    <div class="hero-gold-line"></div>
    <p class="hero-motto-sub">From grit and ethos — the moral courage to do right, regardless.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- scroll indicator removed -->
</section>

<!-- ═══ ORIGIN ═══ -->
<section class="origin">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="origin-text reveal d1">Grithos is not a religion. It is not a replacement for God or faith — it is what happens when faith becomes action. When belief stops being passive and starts being lived. Grithos is the grit that faith produces in a person who refuses to quit.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<!-- ═══ CREED ═══ -->
<section class="creed" id="creed">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="creed-label reveal d1">The Grithos Creed</div>
    <p class="creed-text reveal d2">Do right. Regardless.<br>Own your nature. Live within bounds.<br>Return to the whole.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<!-- ═══ FOUNDATION ═══ -->
<section class="foundation" id="foundation">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal d1" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="sec-label">The Foundation</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">What Grithos Stands On</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal d2">
      <p class="foundation-text">A rational God exists who authored the bounds underlying all things. God is architect, not manager. The bounds God created are real, consistent, and trustworthy. However you choose to honor God is yours. What Grithos asks is that you also align — with the bounds, with virtue, and with the life you were given.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<!-- ═══ TODAY'S PRACTICE ═══ -->
<section class="today-practice" id="today">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="today-card reveal d1">
